data.description: ***Seller has an Assumable VA loan at 3.25%****This is a charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, end unit property with a range of attractive features. The home is equipped with high-quality Pella windows offering great natural light. The living room is enhanced with custom bookcases, adding both functionality and decorative elements. Entertaining is a breeze with a convenient wet bar in the dining room perfect for hosting guests. With an oversized en-suite primary bedroom is generously sized and includes space for a cozy reading nook. The home has generous storage throughout ensuring your belongings can be neatly organized. Lastly, the oversized (26'x26') brick patio with a charming 10'x10' pergola, creates an inviting space for outdoor relaxation and gatherings. The HOA monthly fee covers the exterior of the townhouse, including water/sewer and internet service and an amazing community pool! Come take a look!
